# OpenPraxis dashboard v2 — Vite + Svelte build artifacts.
#
# dist/ rules:
#   - Ignore the actual hashed assets (noisy diffs every build)
#   - BUT keep dist/index.html as a committed stub so `go:embed` always
#     has something to embed on a fresh checkout. `make build` runs
#     `npm run build` before `go build` so the stub gets overwritten
#     with real assets at every Go build.
#   - Also keep dist/.gitkeep so the directory itself survives in git.
node_modules/
dist/*
!dist/index.html
!dist/.gitkeep
*.log
.DS_Store
